snippet.title: Alto’s Adventure – Launch Trailer – Out now for iOS, Android, and Kindle Fire
snippet.description:
Alto’s Adventure is an endless snowboarding odyssey, set against a beautiful and ever changing alpine landscape. 

App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/altos...
Google Play: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.noodlecake.altosadventure
Kindle Fire: http://www.amazon.com/gp/mas/dl/android?p=com.noodlecake.altosadventure
